{"tid":1801063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"失明律師陸小姐: 與其畀佢哋（警察）再亂咁射盲人哋對眼，不如射我，反正我都盲。","createTime":"2019-12-28T11:03:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T11:52:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bc34482cedf679f4ba98a436426f84d4a3c8dcb4","tid":1801063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:03:06.000Z","msg":"下午再有市民發起在「上水和你 Shop」，大批防暴和便衣到場拘捕多人。<br />\n<br />\n多次身處抗爭前線的失明律師陸小姐亦有到場，並在警方的防線附近用牧童笛吹《願榮光歸香港》。陸小姐表示，香港人一直爭取逾半年，政府仍拒絕回應訴求，所以一定會繼續站出來，她又表示她亦是香港人，除了關心殘障人士權益，亦不會無視社會不公，例如愈來愈過份的警暴，「與其畀佢哋（警察）再亂咁射盲人哋對眼，不如射我，反正我都盲。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLwv9vw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLwv9vw.jpg&h=0aa4fee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: 立場Facebook"},{"pid":"2114cce513711b79ecc70dae71ea17212b7f2fe5","tid":1801063,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"睇到片佢坐係班POPO前面<br />\n好撚勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7c009367121109c39b7c5de4a86ae59d393d6e","tid":1801063,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"見過真人<br />\n<br />\n超nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298135d80335d4342190b446961a96f79dba52a8","tid":1801063,"uid":124711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"Respect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e4bbddbc0105badaa757ce69f05ccfc1ff273b","tid":1801063,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm